{{see|Episcopalian}}
==English==
===Adjective===
'''episcopalian'''

# Of or relating to [[bishop]]s of whatever church.
#: ''A bishop is entitled to certain episcopalian privileges.''

===Usage note===
* In the adjectival sense, ''episcopal'' (uncapitalized) will generally do just as well: ''A bishop is entitled to certain episcopal privileges.''

